latestPosts.caption:
LuLu Fashion Week 2025 – Where Style Came Alive! 👠✨

For four stylish days, LuLu Mall Trivandrum became the hub of fashion, culture, and creativity. From trendsetting runway shows to inspiring conversations, the event opened up a bold new world of fashion right at the heart of Kerala.

Thank you to everyone who lived the moment with us. The fashion may fade, but the vibe stays on at @lulumalltvm ❤️

#lulumalltvm #trivandrum #lulumalltrivandrum #lulumall #LuLuFashionWeek2025 #FashionDestination

🎬✨ Kozhikode witnessed its first-ever edition of LuLu Fashion Week — and what an unforgettable journey it was!

Despite unpredictable weather and a hundred moving parts, our team stood strong — From sketching the first poster design to late-night marketing plans, from building the stage to managing the backstage chaos, from running console operations to capturing and editing every perfect frame — this was teamwork in its truest form.
What the audience saw was a stunning show.
What we lived was countless hours of teamwork, passion, problem-solving, and pure dedication.

#LuLuFashionWeek #LuLuMallKozhikode #behindthescenesphotography
